Kamakailan ay mayroon ako

00:17:55.960 --> 00:17:57.070
isang katulad na kaso.

00:17:57.070 --> 00:17:58.600
Sabay ko silang hahawakan.

00:17:59.540 --> 00:18:00.870
Sige, hayaan mo na ako.

00:18:00.960 --> 00:18:01.480
Okay.

